          "link": "https://www.marwoodgroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Marwood-Group-MedTech-Funding-Mandate-May-2021.pdf",
          "snippet": " This has prompted policymakers to adopt a more prescriptive approach: the MedTech Funding Mandate.\n\nIn this note we explore how the MedTech Funding Mandate policy works and explain how Marwood can support those involved and interested in medical technologies understand the key demand drivers, including how local commissioners think about new technology adoption and the returns they seek for the NHS.\n\nThe MedTech Funding Mandate policy aims to accelerate the uptake of innovative medical devices, diagnostics, and digital products by mandating and monitoring the adoption of selected technologies.\n\nThis is a unique opportunity for innovative products to penetrate the NHS market, improving access to NHS services, supporting clinicians to deliver high quality care, and helping patients to better manage their health.\n\n\n\nSource: NHS England, Marwood Group Analysis Note: MedTech Funding Mandate (MTFM)\n",
